  "title": "MARKETING!!",
  "description": "<h2>You + ambition + training = 👀🔥</h2><h2>We’re hiring in Sales & Marketing</h2><h2>No experience needed</h2><h2>Apply before you overthink it</h2><p><br />🚀 <strong>WE’RE HIRING — SALES & MARKETING (NOT YOUR TYPICAL 9–5)</strong></p><p>Thinking about switching careers?<br />Or just done with jobs that don’t teach you anything new?</p><p>If you’re curious, motivated, and want to build real skills in sales & marketing—this might be your sign 👀<br />No experience? That’s fine. We care more about your mindset than your résumé.</p><h3>👀 Who This Is For</h3><p>• People who are self-driven and actually want to grow<br />• Team players who enjoy working with people (not hiding behind a screen)<br />• Anyone curious about leadership and long-term career progression<br />• Fresh grads & career switchers—yes, you’re welcome here</p><h3>💼 What You’ll Be Doing</h3><p>• Learning real-world, ethical sales & marketing skills (the useful kind)<br />• Working with a team on campaigns for well-known brands<br />• Building genuine relationships with clients and customers<br />• Developing leadership skills as you progress</p><h3>🎯 What You’ll Get Out of It</h3><p>• Hands-on training with constant support<br />• Clear, performance-based growth (your effort actually matters)<br />• Opportunities for local & overseas exposure 🌍<br />• A team that mentors, supports, and wants to see you win</p><h3>📩 Sound Like You?</h3><p>Send in your résumé and apply now.</p><p>🤫 <em>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted—don’t scroll past your next opportunity.</em></p>",
